<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/24(Thu.)A Day in the Life of a Sustainable Minimalist/Is Your Stuff Stopping You(Host:Nikki)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=327&amp;p=343#p343"><![CDATA[
Session I. A Day in the Life of a Sustainable Minimalist<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/LUpyStqP_1Q">https://youtu.be/LUpyStqP_1Q</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. Have you ever chosen to change your lifestyle? Why?<br />2. Do you think life with less stuff is boring? Why or why not?<br />3. Have you ever bought something that you thought would make you happy, but didn't?  Share some examples with us.<br />4. What are you not buying anymore?<br /><br />Session II. Is Your Stuff Stopping You?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/8Pb-hjqdjbY">https://youtu.be/8Pb-hjqdjbY</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. Do you or friends accumulate things? What are they? Why? <br />2. Do experiences make us happier than possessions/ stuff?  What’s your opinion?<br />3. Why do you like to buy things? What does buying make you feel?<br />4. How do you organize your life/ house/ work?<br /><br />Extended reading: <br />The Joy of Less:  <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/iGHzqmnGH4A">https://youtu.be/iGHzqmnGH4A</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Suggested Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. Free talk<br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. First topic discussion<br />8:10 p.m. --8:40 p.m. Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:40 p.m.-- 9.:15 p.m. Second topic discussion<br />9:15 p.m.-- 9:30 p.m. Presentation (Participants that haven't presented yet are invited)<br /><br />speaker time: 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time: 3 minutes<br /><br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第三區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Sun Oct 20, 2019 2:16 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
